text.tspan: n : Valid if e=1 and s=1, otherwise 0; indicates the number of
bytes that do not contain data (bytes 8-n to 7 do not contain data)
e : Transfer type, 0 = normal transfer, 1 = expedited transfer
s : Size indicator, 0 = data set size not indicated, 1= data set size indicated
index & subindex : Reflect the OD address to be accessed
